{"favorite_id": 10140, "calc_type": "calculator", "dosing": false, "full_title_en": "GCS-Pupils Score", "short_title_en": "GCS-Pupils Score", "medium_description_en": "<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-32be6d1a-7fff-8624-2674-b4aa6d99fae0\">Combines GCS and pupil reactivity for greater accuracy at low GCS.", "short_description_en": "GCS incorporating pupil reactivity.", "before_use": "", "instructions_en": "", "purpose_en": ["Prognosis"], "disease_en": ["Trauma", "Traumatic Brain Injury"], "specialty_en": ["Surgery (Trauma)", "Neurology", "Neurosurgery", "Critical Care", "Emergency Medicine"], "chief_complaint_en": ["Injury/Trauma", "Head Injury"], "system_en": ["Neurologic"], "search_abbreviation_en": ["tbi", "GCS", "Glasgow Coma Scale", "pediatric Glasgow Coma Scale", "pGCS", "GCS pupil", "GCS pupils", "pupil reactivity"], "slug": "gcs-pupils-score", "seo": {"meta_description_en": "The GCS-Pupils Score combines GCS and pupil reactivity for greater accuracy.", "keywords_en": "Glasgow Coma Scale, pediatric Glasgow Coma Scale, pGCS, GCS, GCS pupils, GCS pupil, pupil reactivity"}, "content": {"how_to_use": {"use_case_en": "<p>Patients with traumatic brain injury.</p>", "pearls_pitfalls_en": "<ul>\n<li>Retrospectively derived, based on pooled data from two large databases, IMPACT and CRASH.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Addition of pupil data was shown to be particularly useful at very low GCS&nbsp;scores (3-4), likely because&nbsp;of higher frequency of abnormal pupil response in patients with severe&nbsp;TBI and low GCS (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29631516\" target=\"_blank\">Brennan 2018</a>).</li>\n</ul>", "why_use_en": ""}, "next_steps": {"advice_en": "<p>The GCS-Pupils Score is not intended to replace the GCS as a&nbsp;snapshot of&nbsp;an individual patient's condition and how it changes over time; the authors state it is meant to act as a supplement to add information about&nbsp;severity and prognosis (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29631516\" target=\"_blank\">Brennan 2018</a>).</p>", "management_en": "", "critical_actions_en": ""}, "about": {"formula_en": "<p dir=\"ltr\">GCS-Pupils Score = <calculator id=\"64\">GCS Score</calculator> - Pupil response,</p>\n<p>where GCS Score = Eye response + Verbal response + Motor response</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">and other variables are as follows:<br /></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"94\" /><col width=\"195\" /><col width=\"83\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Variable</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Points</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"5\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Eye response</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Eyes open spontaneously</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">4</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Eye opening to verbal command</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Eye opening to pain</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">No eye opening</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Not assessable (trauma, edema, etc.)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"6\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Verbal response</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Oriented</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">5</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Confused</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">4</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Inappropriate words</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Incomprehensible sounds</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">No verbal response</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Intubated</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"6\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Motor response</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Obeys commands</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">6</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Localizes pain</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">5</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Withdrawal from pain</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">4</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Flexion to pain</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Extension to pain</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">No motor response</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Pupil response</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Both pupils unreactive to light</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">One pupil unreactive to light</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Both pupils reactive to light (normal)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>", "more_info_en": "<p></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"*\" /><col width=\"*\" /><col width=\"*\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>GCS-Pupils Score</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Mortality at 6 months post-injury</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Unfavorable outcome (vegetative state or severe disability) at 6 months post-injury</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">74.45%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">89.59%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">64.62%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">85.22%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">40.92%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">65.53%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">4</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">39.47%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">68.90%</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">5</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">32.57%</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">57.75%</p>\n</t